Data Science Job

One job that involves data science is Data Scientist in this lower levels of this job you are mainly doing Data Wrangling and Data visualization. These tasks are mainly focused on turning raw data into a form that can be used for analysis and create the first graphs and chart that can be used to interpret the data.
